      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions replicated in simulation within stated uncertainty bounds; inlet flow profiles and fluid temperature documented.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles were taken from manufacturer data rather than direct measurement. Temperature control during experiments was not reported, introducing unquantified thermal boundary condition uncertainty."
    },
