      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative validation metric (e.g., E% or validation uncertainty Uval) computed for hemolysis index across all 5 operating points with statistical significance.",
      "rationale": "Comparison was performed at 3 of 5 operating points. No formal validation uncertainty metric was computed; only qualitative agreement was reported. Two high-speed operating points are unvalidated."
