      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted at VAD operating conditions (flow rates 3–6 L/min, rotational speeds 2400–3600 RPM) with blood-analog fluid of matched viscosity.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments used water-glycerol analog at 25°C rather than blood-analog at physiological temperature. Operating speed range covered only 2400–3000 RPM, missing the upper VAD envelope."
